{"tid":1838113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東省新增21宗新型肺炎個案　至今累計53宗確診","createTime":"2020-01-24T01:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T02:54:15.000Z","uid":226984,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0a246c958ceffba3e064e113601c850208c77605","tid":1838113,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"廣東衛健委公布，昨日新增21宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案，陽江和清遠首次有確診病例，分別有3宗和1宗，廣東至今累計確診病例53宗。<br />\n<br />\n其他6個有新增病例的城市，包括廣州、珠海、佛山、韶關、惠州和中山。<br />\n<br />\n在累計確診個案中，45宗在發病前曾經在湖北居住或者旅遊，6宗是湖北輸入病例的家屬，1宗與武漢朋友聚餐，1宗沒有明顯接觸史，目前沒有醫護人員感染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504572-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504572-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=e260ea4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504572-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=62b8e9a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504572-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2ac881f1044e8c0c88d641170d5aa9b0278e95e0","tid":1838113,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:11:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ea0e4dba17aaae7afddeb34437ebe23a2aae6954","tid":1838113,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:24:49.000Z","msg":"一宗沒有明顯接觸<img src=\"/assets/fa